    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Le Château</strong>（法语中意为“<i>城堡</i>”）是一个微型城市建设游戏，重点展现有限资源和有限空间下的创造力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >适合在时间很少或没有时间的时候玩，但你又有游戏的欲望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/2fbbad3cb28fd53c7ad5f71e30a00f8c.poster.avif?t=1737968851\" width=400 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/2fbbad3cb28fd53c7ad5f71e30a00f8c.webm?t=1737968851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/2fbbad3cb28fd53c7ad5f71e30a00f8c.mp4?t=1737968851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将你的王国打造成1块瓷砖大小，或者扩展至11x11块瓷砖大小，享受多种不同色调的美学体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/cb5b089ec8eb0b8dfbd78bb50cd2cff3.poster.avif?t=1737968851\" width=400 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/cb5b089ec8eb0b8dfbd78bb50cd2cff3.webm?t=1737968851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/cb5b089ec8eb0b8dfbd78bb50cd2cff3.mp4?t=1737968851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>特点</strong></i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 多种世界形状</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 数十种不同类型的可供选择的对象</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 6 种不同的颜色调色板</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 对你的王国大小有完全控制权</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 随着更多地块填充，世界慢慢变得生动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 青蛙</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Le Château 没有真正的目标。只是在建立梦想中的王国时有很多自由！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受 Paul Shnepf 的《The Block》启发</p>",
